    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/b0b305b5b12ea3cc91dda2fe4785b33a.avif?t=1753803463\" width=800 height=171 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three different game modes</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Normal, Scrambled, and Trivia</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scrambled and Trivia modes offer hints to help you if you get stuck</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each mode can be played as a 15- or 30-second challenge</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully customizable games</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose country names or capitals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select one or more of 6 different continents</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are over 200 countries and territories with their own flags</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose if you want to view maps, flags or why not both</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want more challenge? Enable case-sensitive</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Detailed statistics</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Track every keystroke with precision</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High score lists</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more..</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/5a17a997fc4859ff6fcb1e0381c68a89.avif?t=1753803463\" width=800 height=171 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/47cfb8e7ca43ef44a5b9f25cc75ffb0a.poster.avif?t=1753803463\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/47cfb8e7ca43ef44a5b9f25cc75ffb0a.webm?t=1753803463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/47cfb8e7ca43ef44a5b9f25cc75ffb0a.mp4?t=1753803463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the world at your own pace by viewing each country's map, flag, and name. Type in the country or capital to practice your knowledge. You can focus on one or more continents for a customized experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/cc682d0ac438795a4d5e0e012ed53a19.avif?t=1753803463\" width=800 height=171 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/60e5be4239fe314472e01d819f037f78.poster.avif?t=1753803463\" width=800 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/60e5be4239fe314472e01d819f037f78.webm?t=1753803463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/60e5be4239fe314472e01d819f037f78.mp4?t=1753803463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your speed and focus by unscrambling the letters. If you get stuck, don’t worry.. you’ll have reveal hints and shuffle hints to help you out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/1cff253e13e934c517c04c0685cbcba2.avif?t=1753803463\" width=800 height=171 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/8fd81124bc66036be133884b992346f8.poster.avif?t=1753803463\" width=800 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/8fd81124bc66036be133884b992346f8.webm?t=1753803463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136690/extras/8fd81124bc66036be133884b992346f8.mp4?t=1753803463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself by guessing the names of countries or their capitals without any labels. If you get stuck, don’t worry.. you’ll have hints available that can reveal the next few letters to assist you! </p>",
